listings.comment: Yan was an absolute pleasure to work with, this is the first website ive built and i had no idea what i wanted i spoke to 5 people before going with yan, most werent responsive or didnt put the effort to explain certain things in detail yan did, he was very responsive and went into great detail and even gave me examples of websites to help me figure out what style website i woud like ect.. he was quick and fast, im extremly happy i chose yan, he was great and i look forward to working with him on future projects!!!

Yan was extremely prompt and professional. I had a couple of additional edits and he addressed them straight away and worked with me to ensure my website was styled correctly and mobile responsive. Highly recommend working with him! Thank you for everything Yan!

Yan is great!  He really elevated my site to the next level. I went with someone before him and was very unhappy. I’m glad I found Yan! Definitely using him again in the near future. Highly recommend!
I've enjoyed working with Yan. This is the 3rd website that he has worked on for me. He is really skilled at what he offers and goes above and beyond. I will use his services again. Highly recommend.

Working with Yan Mirza was an EXCEPTIONAL experience! His attention to detail and professionalism in website development truly exceeded my expectations. Yan's proactive communication and politeness made the process seamless—he really went above and beyond. 🤩
